{"tid":2226213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"智障人士被黑警濫捕 情緒失控喺狗屋做出自殘行為","createTime":"2020-10-02T01:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T07:03:06.000Z","uid":321059,"like":544,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"66ecc1c9f2ac3ed884febbcdace9bacb1365469a","tid":2226213,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"【防暴警察知道智障人士在十．一被捕時有多害怕嗎？】<br />\n文：陣地連線社工@香港社會工作者總工會<br />\n<br />\n10月1日的晚上8時45分，我收到朋友Whatsapp通知，姨婆及彥仔與朋友在銅鑼灣飯聚後被捕，急需社工前往支援，<span class=\"orange\">因為姨婆是一位有腰患的長者，她的姨甥彥仔則患有長期病患，也是一位輕度智障人士，每晚也需要服藥和打針，以避免情緒激動和暈眩。</span><br />\n<br />\n#無情也無奈的拘捕<br />\n認識姨婆多年，她一直也是一位性格爽朗的長者。可是，<span class=\"orange\">這晚姨婆獲釋放後，卻不斷說對不起，不斷說不好意思打擾大家於中秋節與家人團聚，也說自己有告訴防暴警員自己和彥仔只是與朋友在附近飯聚，也告訴防暴警察彥仔是一名有長期病患的智障人士，可惜最後仍被拘捕。</span>看見姨婆的「抱歉」，內心感到很心痛和難受，為何要一位年邁照顧者承擔這份不需要的壓力？<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n零晨1:20，當大家也十分焦急他們何時可以獲釋，因為彥仔已過了打針的時間很久，情緒狀況有機會不穩，我突然被警察召見入去。<span class=\"orange\">原來彥仔在房間內情緒激動，不斷想襲擊身邊的人，也想破壞身邊的東西，更想撞頭傷害自己。</span>那一刻，我唯有叫一眾警察退後，親身協助激動的彥仔冷靜，避免他受到傷害。那一刻姨婆不在附近，警察說彥仔襲擊姨婆，所以要將姨婆和彥仔分開。我於彥仔稍為冷靜後，要求警察帶姨婆返來，讓我可了解彥仔的狀況是否需要入院。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n零晨1:50，我們終於可以離開警署，但彥仔的情緒仍然激動，<span class=\"orange\">不斷想衝出馬路，大家要合力讓他上車。如果只有姨婆一人，又如何讓力大無窮的彥仔回家呢？在車上不斷聽到姨婆說抱歉，但這是她和彥仔的錯嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKSocialWorkersGeneralUnion/photos/a.731466150242473/3305790362810026/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKSocialWorkersGeneralUnion%2Fphotos%2Fa.731466150242473%2F3305790362810026%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdApR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=50564ab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKSocialWorkersGeneralUnion/photos/a.731466150242473/3305790362810026/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"52aaf1de2ef4fab795ba536cc7c6d1e9885efdd6","tid":2226213,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c601acb9934f2fe4ddf511c2136ff9cfb0a0da","tid":2226213,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f03b35bb038c23afa754c390e77b72f1907a75c","tid":2226213,"uid":40625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f8e40c9a8be81f1ba90c08efd7c788155c7780","tid":2226213,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1533a21f347c4a409970ab9fce50d237b419b5c3","tid":2226213,"uid":321059,"like":330,"dislike":4,"score":326,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:50:29.000Z","msg":"mon po狗可唔可以解釋下<br />\n一個智障人士同一個身體行動不便婆婆<br />\n點樣可以做出挑釁性行為從而干犯非法集結？"},{"pid":"caddb5cef53c66946798e15207b8d8f49ee336e4","tid":2226213,"uid":12991,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:51:43.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n自己搞唔撚掂就拿拿臨放甩身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc83e4dd19e1afe468fbf9a67cd85ed23db8e9ba","tid":2226213,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bafe90eb58945385e8fe0be24115ee68358838","tid":2226213,"uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"綠狗亂鳩咁咬玩死狗屋d狗"},{"pid":"2a8242f47002dae3187e70a205c1b77c68ea5f06","tid":2226213,"uid":321059,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score"